<div style="background: var(--cream);">
  <div class="reviews-section" id="reviews">
    <div class="reviews-hero-img reveal">
      <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AppaaThe/Rituel-store/main/product-images/rituel-guasha-closeup-inuse.png" alt="Close-up of amethyst gua sha stone being used on face" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <div class="reviews-header">
      <span class="section-label reveal">Verified Buyers</span>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1">They stopped asking<br><em>if she lost weight.</em></h2>
      <p class="reviews-sub reveal reveal-delay-2">She hadn't lost a pound. It was the ritual.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="reviews-grid">

      <div class="review-card reveal">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"People kept asking if I lost weight. I hadn't lost a pound. That's when I realised it was the gua sha. My face just doesn't puff up like it used to."</p>
        <p class="review-author">Sofia M. — Brussels, Verified Buyer</p>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"Skeptical at first — I've been burned by every serum on the market. Now I genuinely panic if I forget to do it. The ritual aspect is what makes you stick with it. My skin texture has completely changed."</p>
        <p class="review-author">Camille R. — Paris, Verified Buyer</p>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"The ice roller after a late night is genuinely magic. I look awake and glowing in 5 minutes flat. My mum noticed before I said a word. I've gifted this to my sister, my mum, and my best friend."</p>
        <p class="review-author">Aisha K. — Amsterdam, Verified Buyer</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="reviews-money-quote reveal">
      <div class="money-quote-inner">
        <div class="money-quote-mark">&ldquo;</div>
        <p class="money-quote-text">I did this every morning for 3 months. My jawline is more defined than it's been in years. My dentist even noticed my sinuses had cleared. Once you start — you will not want to skip a morning. The difference is too obvious.</p>
        <div class="money-quote-author">
          <span class="money-quote-name">Léa V.</span>
          <span class="money-quote-detail">Antwerp · Verified Buyer · Full Ritual Set</span>
        </div>
        <div class="review-stars" style="font-size:14px; margin-top: 12px;">★★★★★</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Testimonials",
  "presets": [{ "name": "Testimonials" }]
}
{% endschema %}
